*ximian-connector-1.4.7.2 (05 Aug 2004)

  05 Aug 2004; Alastair Tse <liquidx@gentoo.org>
  ximian-connector-1.4.5.0.6.1.ebuild, ximian-connector-1.4.6.0.6.1.ebuild,
  +ximian-connector-1.4.7.2.ebuild:
  New GPL licensed ximian connector. initial ebuild thanks to Sourav Mandal
  <sourav@sourav.net> (#50801)

  07 Jun 2004; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org>
  ximian-connector-1.2.2_p1.ebuild:
